vDOC is a next-generation solution for health at your home. An estimated 78% of the hospital visits, which are non-emergency medical conditions, can be served using the vDOC platform. It enables patients to search and choose physicians from the pool of BMDC-certified physicians linked with the vDOC platform. An individual can search a physician based on the specialty symptoms, and also location. We aim to connect Patients and Doctors Face-to-Face – Any Time, Any Place. Users can connect with physicians using a mobile device, tablet, or computer (P2P). Patients can also book an appointment, search nearby hospitals, ambulance, pharmacies, and access to healthcare tips and articles.
